site_name: Harlequin F C Stoop Memorial Ground

protected_spaces_details.description: Outdoor sports facilities incl school playing fields

description: 1. Demolition of existing West Stand and groundsmans's house and other ancillary buildings on the western side of the ground. Removal of two main floodlighting columns on western side of pitch and floodlighting on practice pitch behind East Stand. 2. Construction of a replacement stand with capacity for 3,881 spectators with ancillary facilities, including players' and officials' facilities, club offices, club shop, a Members bar, 13 corporate hospitality boxes, an Executive Club and two lounges. 3. Construction of a residential development comprising a four-storey block of 67 flats on part of the open land behind the existing East Stand, with basement parking. 4. Use of remainder land behind the East Stand as public open space.
site_number: Harlequin F C Stoop Memorial Ground
